div.div: We will deploy the application estate onto Google's Cloud Platform. GCP is already in use by the client, within the organization. There are already teams equipped to deal with related GCP issues. This includes existing licensing for the workforce. Adoption of GCP reduces the need to rely on competitors for cloud infrastructure services. The downside is that we will now be dependant on Google Cloud for our infrastructure.
